sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as Operator
    participant Health as Health inspector
    participant Data as Data-access APIs

    Operator->>Health: health()
    Health->>Data: read_daemon_state(channel_gateway, scheduler)
    Data-->>Health: liveness_and_heartbeat
    Health->>Data: read_channel_queue_stats()
    Data-->>Health: backlog_and_oldest_age
    Health->>Data: measure_db_latency()
    Data-->>Health: db_latency
    Health->>Data: read_recent_recorder_and_dream_status()
    Data-->>Health: recent_status
    Health-->>Operator: health_report(status, details)
    Note over Health,Data: Health is read-only and creates no daemon state for one-shot CLIs.
